<blockquote>
<p><strong>Correct answer: a)</strong> $P(B) = 0{,}3 \times 0{,}6 + 0{,}1 \times 0{,}4 = 0{,}18 + 0{,}04 = 0{,}22$.</p>
</blockquote>
