$P(49{,}6 \leq X \leq 50{,}4) = \Phi(2)-\Phi(-2) = 0{,}9772-(1-0{,}9772) = 0{,}9772-0{,}0228 = \mathbf{0{,}9544}$.</p>
</blockquote>
